{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgxc6yx8yjk0","created":1772966563085,"text":"X线机","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxc793js280","created":1772966585234,"text":"诊断用X线机分类","layout":null,"expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxc75k7mjk0","created":1772966577534,"text":"最大输出功率","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxc76k0gbs0","created":1772966579699,"text":"小型","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcakhgyy80","created":1772966845113,"text":"管电流<200mA,管电压90~100kV","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxcabh3ofs0","created":1772966825499,"text":"中型","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcbxqla000","created":1772966952326,"text":"管电流200~500mA,管电压100~125kV","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxcac4boqg0","created":1772966826903,"text":"大型","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcc1y1aag0","created":1772966961484,"text":"管电流>500mA,管电压125~150kV","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxc7806t3s0","created":1772966582854,"text":"高压变压器工作频率","layout":null,"note":"工频:高压变压器工作频率等于供电电源频率\n中/高频:采用了直流逆变技术,也称逆变X线机","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcd0yao0w0","created":1772967037687,"text":"工频X线机","layout":null,"note":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcf4hzpi80","created":1772967202136,"text":"50Hz  or  60Hz","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxcdds0p8g0","created":1772967065605,"text":"中频X线机","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcgd09zts0","created":1772967299021,"text":"400Hz~20kHz","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxcdeq3qtc0","created":1772967067666,"text":"高频X线机","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgxcgrufsow0","created":1772967331319,"text":">20kHz","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt022jwr40","created":1773217100169,"text":"应用范围","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgzto1g5am80","created":1773218979554,"text":"综合型","note":"具有透视、摄影和特殊检查等多种功能","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgzto5f05k00","created":1773218988192,"text":"专用型","layout":null,"note":"P21~P22"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgztp1o1mc00","created":1773219058395,"text":"乳腺摄影X线机","layout":null,"note":"钼靶X线机\n用于乳腺,非金属异物,血管瘤和阴囊等软组织摄影\n1. 管电压调节范围较低,20~50Kv\n2. 使用软X线管以产生软射线\n3. 焦点小(0.1~0.3)\n4. 配用乳腺摄影专用支架,较长的遮线筒"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztphutuls0","created":1773219093634,"text":"牙科X线机","layout":null,"note":"拍摄牙片,输出功率小-采用组合机头.照射范围很小-采用指向性很强的遮线筒.\n管电压:50~70.管电流10~15mA."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztpkmr4ps0","created":1773219099676,"text":"口腔全景X线机","layout":null,"note":"是一种把 曲面分布的颌部 展开排列成一幅图像的一种 体层摄影方法\n"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh4tbik17k00","created":1773725797843,"text":"机架结构","note":"1. 立柱 \n2. 滑架\n3. 转动臂\n4. 头颅测量组件(横臂,头颅固定装置,X线片拖)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh4tbm4lgmg0","created":1773725805617,"text":"类型","note":"1. 单轴转动式\n2. 三轴转动式\n3. 连续可变轴式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgztpyh0pow0","created":1773219129805,"text":"手术用X线机","layout":null,"note":"配有X-TV,主要用于急诊室或手术室的透视(对异物进行定位,观察骨折复位过程及内固定情况)\n车载式---方便移动\nC形臂----方便从各方位接近患者.\n\n1. 多采用中,高频变压器+组合机头\n2. 透视+摄影(功率小  90 Kv   40 mA  以下)\n3. X-TV多配用5\"~7\"影像增强器,两者之间使用光纤直接耦合\n4. 配有TV存储装置,脉冲透视减少剂量,术后回放,DSA功能.\n5. 车架可移动+C形臂"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh4tn1qk4vc0","created":1773726701603,"text":"多采用中,高频变压器+组合机头"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh4tnisndmo0","created":1773726738734,"text":"透视+摄影(功率小  90 Kv   40 mA  以下)"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt02pq4qw0","created":1773217101570,"text":"结构形式","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgztqrfpoww0","created":1773219192852,"text":"便携式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgzts94q3k00","created":1773219309734,"text":"移动式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgzts9mbpuo0","created":1773219310798,"text":"固定式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt02vkqbk0","created":1773217101924,"text":"使用目的","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgzts71g2xk0","created":1773219305182,"text":"透视"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztskjxjuw0","created":1773219334598,"text":"摄影"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztskn3plc0","created":1773219334790,"text":"胃肠"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztskpzj5c0","created":1773219334964,"text":"心血管造影"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt02y6dtk0","created":1773217102081,"text":"高压整流形式","layout":null,"note":"自整流\n单向半波/全波整流\n三相整流（三相六波、三相十二波）————应用于大型心血管造影机、胃肠机等。\n高频逆变整流————目前几乎所有的新式数字化X线机（DR、移动DR、DSA等）都采用这种方式。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgztu78fiow0","created":1773219462333,"text":"单向自整流X线机","note":"主要用于小型、移动式或齿科X线机。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztuajdf9k0","created":1773219469525,"text":"单向半波整流X线机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztuhbzln40","created":1773219484316,"text":"单向全波整流X线机","note":"广泛用于30kW以下的中型X线机，如胃肠机、普通拍片机。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgztvuxm6bc0","created":1773219592286,"text":"倍压整流X线机"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt0310dpk0","created":1773217102252,"text":" ","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgzt00zljoo0","created":1773217097813,"text":"构成 ","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0xyfm1nwg0","created":1773332638423,"text":"主机"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0xynlpfmo0","created":1773332655817,"text":"X线管装置","note":"是X线装置的核心部件,产生X射线.\n","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh4w5p9qf1s0","created":1773733805604,"text":"种类","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0y6vdvf340","created":1773333299671,"text":"气体电离式X线管"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y75vp8tc0","created":1773333322517,"text":"固定阳极X线管","note":"高真空热阴极固定阳极X线管\n特点: 功率小,焦点大.\n目前仅用于低功率的移动式和牙科X线机中"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh4w2ck7stc0","created":1773733542846,"text":"阳极","note":"阻挡高速运动的电子流而产生X线并将产生的热量传到出去.\n吸收二次射线和散射线."},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kcsbcmk00","created":1773802067418,"text":"阳极头"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kd52n9jc0","created":1773802095190,"text":"靶面","note":"钨制成(熔点3370度,原子序数74)\n钨靶的熔点高,发射率高,厚1.5~3.0mm.长方形或正方形.\n钨靶采用**真空焊接**的方法和导热率较高的无氧实心铜体连接"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh5kd78k6io0","created":1773802099901,"text":"铜体","note":"导热率较高"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh5kcuzvzwg0","created":1773802073255,"text":"阳极罩","note":"又称阳极帽\n固定在阳极头上,由无氧铜制成\n纵轴方向的圆形开口对准阴极灯丝,X线出口处同为圆形开口.\n主要作用:吸收二次电子(约57%)和散射线"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh5kcxtwvig0","created":1773802079424,"text":"阳极柄","note":"紫铜制成,与阳极头的铜体相连\n将阳极靶面的热量传导出去,传送高电亚至阳极端."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh5kd192p7k0","created":1773802086871,"text":"玻璃圈","note":"可伐圈\n阳极和玻璃管壳过渡连续部分.\n膨胀圈(铁镍钴合金制成)+玻璃喇叭"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh4w2ehej140","created":1773733547029,"text":"阴极","note":"作用:发射热电子和聚焦."},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5rd5fmb740","created":1773821843743,"text":"灯丝","note":"钨丝,绕成螺旋管状.\n#### 高温下的特点\n\t1. 发射电子\n    2. 熔点高,不易蒸发\n    3. 延伸性好,不易变形\n#### 双焦点\n\t* 大焦点:发射较多的电子,大的管电流,用于曝光条件较大的部位,图像清晰度低\n    * 小焦点:发射较少的电子,小的管电流,用于图像清晰度要求高的部位.\n    * 三根引线:(零线)一根为大,小焦点灯丝的公共引线,(火线)另外两根分别为大,小焦点灯丝的引线.\n#### 电\n\t* 灯丝两端电压为5~10V(50Hz)的交流电.\n    * 灯丝温度达到约2100K后开始发射电子\n    * 一定范围内,kV,mA越大,灯丝温度越高,灯丝发射的电子越多.\n    * 灯丝加热电压超过额定值5%时,灯丝寿命减少一半."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh5rd73usfc0","created":1773821847386,"text":"集射罩","note":"铁或铁镍合金制成的圆弧直槽或阶梯直槽,灯丝位于其中,使电子聚焦到阳极靶面,并吸收大部分二次电子而保护灯丝和玻璃管壳."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh5rddhhmsg0","created":1773821861271,"text":"玻璃管壳","note":"用耐高温,绝缘度高,膨胀系数小的钼玻璃制成,支撑阳极和阴极并保持管内高真空."},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y7b6yyi00","created":1773333334082,"text":"旋转阳极X线管","note":"特点: 功率大(20~150kW),焦点小(有效焦点:1mmX1mm,2mmX2mm.微焦点:0.3mmX0.3mm).\n阴极灯丝偏离X线管长轴中心对准阳极环形靶面.\n"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh4w4k876cw0","created":1773733716262,"text":"旋转阳极盘及靶面","note":"早期阳极盘由纯钨制成,用短的钼杆支撑盘中心,后改为铼钨合金的靶面和钼+石墨的盘基.\n6~21度倾斜角."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh6eleisqao0","created":1773887375968,"text":"转子","note":"无氧铜制成,通过钼杆与阳极盘连接,表面做了黑化处理.\n为防止靶面融化,设有启动电路,延时电路,保护电路.\n低转速3000r/min\n高转速9000r/min\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh6eli2z8ig0","created":1773887383718,"text":"转轴和轴承"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh6elldpnrc0","created":1773887390898,"text":"管壳","note":"用质硬,耐热,耐高压,能承受机械压力的玻璃制成.\nX线射出的出口处玻璃较薄---较少X线衰减.\n升华现象导致第二阳极---损害X线管\n两端用玻璃中间用金属的管壳可解决升华现象(金属管壳第一层窗口为玻璃,第二层为铝).\n之后又研究出金属陶瓷X线管."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y7r6chao0","created":1773333368873,"text":"三极X线管","note":"阳极,阴极,控制栅极.\n在栅极和灯丝之间加入负电场(-5~-2kV),运用电场力阻止热电子飞向阳极来控制X线的产生和消失.\n三极X线管的X线的产生和消失很突然,脉冲几乎为方波,X线质好,可以瞬时启动和瞬时曝光."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y7ubfrjs0","created":1773333375711,"text":"软X线管","note":"钼靶,金属铍作为X线窗口材料.多用于乳腺等软组织摄影.\nX线波长0.06~0.09nm,由(20~40kV)电压产生的热电子撞击钼靶引起的 **光电效应**产生.\nX线图像对比度较高.\n"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh6j6q2qigo0","created":1773900331205,"text":"钼靶","note":"原子序数42,熔点2622摄氏度.\n近年采用钼-铑/钒/钨制成的靶面.\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh6j8644ecg0","created":1773900444482,"text":"铍窗","note":"软X射线易通过,用钼片0.03mm进行滤过."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh6j88k2t5s0","created":1773900449800,"text":"极间距离","note":"因管电压较低,缩短阴,阳极之间"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh4w63anqlc0","created":1773733836134,"text":"X线管管套"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh4w7p7p1c00","created":1773733962208,"text":"X线管冷却"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh4w7rqikpc0","created":1773733967699,"text":"X线管焦点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh4w81k1ppk0","created":1773733989076,"text":"X线管的特性与参数"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0xyrbsu2o0","created":1773332663925,"text":"高压发生装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0yqwiicrk0","created":1773334869411,"text":"高压变压器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yqzqwjaw0","created":1773334876449,"text":"X线管灯丝变压器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yr63fleg0","created":1773334890268,"text":"高压硅堆"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yrd4qpk80","created":1773334905584,"text":"高压变换闸"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yxabfzow0","created":1773335369644,"text":"高压电缆"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yxc08xhc0","created":1773335373321,"text":"充放电高压发生装置","note":"电容,电阻"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0xyu8wxo00","created":1773332670281,"text":"控制装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0yxvdeths0","created":1773335415476,"text":"电源开关"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yxxp1jjs0","created":1773335420532,"text":"电源电压调节器及电压表"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yy7qy6940","created":1773335442415,"text":"管电压调节器及管电压表"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yym231jk0","created":1773335473564,"text":"管电流调节器及管电流表"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yys5o4pc0","created":1773335486841,"text":"曝光控制及指示器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yywbwy000","created":1773335495926,"text":"容量保护装置及指示器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yz4egz940","created":1773335513495,"text":"透视放射量限制器"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0xyijqg6g0","created":1773332644814,"text":"外围装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0y4q39gtc0","created":1773333131417,"text":"机械装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0y9umbmjs0","created":1773333533098,"text":"诊视床","note":"床身里卧功能: +90度~-30度\t\t\t\n床面移动功能:床面能电动伸出,水平时可向头测伸出50~100cm,足侧20~50cm.\t\t\n点片架移动功能:手动移动,由电磁止锁器控制.\n(医学影像设备学 P18)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0yzmg4e600","created":1773335552777,"text":"荧光屏式诊视床","note":"床体(底座,床身,床面)\n点片架(上有荧光屏)\n点片架平衡装置\n动力系统\n\n\n床身回转动力系统\n床面移动动力系统"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yzrb8cz40","created":1773335563365,"text":"X-TV式诊视床"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yzvs0fzk0","created":1773335573087,"text":"特殊诊视床"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0z00xmdbc0","created":1773335584310,"text":"遥控床","note":"X-TV和诊视床的组合,实现全自动化透视的新型诊视床\n床下X线管式:暗盒式点片架\n床上X线管式:无暗盒式点片架"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z03tc5s00","created":1773335590581,"text":"摇篮床","note":"功能全面,自动化程度更高的遥控床,\n多采用固定底座和C形滑槽\n(医学影像设备学P19)"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ya08msgw0","created":1773333545331,"text":"摄影床与立式摄影架","note":"摄影床由床架和床面组成,床面下配置有活动式滤线器称为滤线器摄影床\n立式摄影架主要用于胸部X线摄影---胸片架,部分配有\"长焦距,高栅比\"的固定/活动滤线栅."},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ywcwclqg0","created":1773335296898,"text":"普通摄影床"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ywfydz7c0","created":1773335303551,"text":"间接摄影床"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ywiiyizk0","created":1773335309149,"text":"体层摄影床"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ywlughk00","created":1773335316374,"text":"特殊摄影床"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ya2eilxk0","created":1773333550040,"text":"X线管组件支持装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ybipwteo0","created":1773333663922,"text":"立柱式支持装置","note":"落地式支持装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0yd07yaeo0","created":1773333780382,"text":"双地轨式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yd55xcls0","created":1773333791143,"text":"天地轨式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0yd7umrxk0","created":1773333796991,"text":"摄影床一体化式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ybqn5uzc0","created":1773333681170,"text":"悬吊式支持装置","note":"固定纵向天轨\n移动横向天轨\n滑车\n伸缩架(弹簧-塔轮-滑轮),圆柱式弹簧/盘簧式弹簧\n横臂\n控制盒"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ybvutcns0","created":1773333692516,"text":"C型臂式支持装置"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y4s0etn40","created":1773333135598,"text":"影像装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ya4u4ads0","created":1773333555337,"text":"X线电影机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z0cfbagg0","created":1773335609324,"text":"X-TV"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z0eikwpc0","created":1773335613875,"text":"点片照相机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z0hzmjn40","created":1773335621436,"text":"X线录像机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z0kj8ooo0","created":1773335626976,"text":"荧光屁IP,FPD"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0y4uzqzs00","created":1773333142089,"text":"配套装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0z0vm07t40","created":1773335651088,"text":"激光照相机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z0y0neww0","created":1773335656327,"text":"X线胶片自动洗片机"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z1bhs4p40","created":1773335685661,"text":"立体观片灯"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z1i32d9c0","created":1773335700008,"text":"遮线器","note":"又名:缩光器.\n安装在X线管管套窗口位置,控制X线照射野的大小和形状.\n内设光源和反射镜---模拟X线管焦点位置."},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0z3fmkio80","created":1773335851386,"text":"遮线板","note":"管套窗口附加一块铅板"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1elt6vxyo0","created":1773379608116,"text":"遮线筒","note":"铁板制成的圆柱,圆锥,放椎形的筒,内壁附有铅板"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1elv5kw280","created":1773379612391,"text":"活动遮线器","note":"两块能开闭的铅板,分两层垂直排列","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1enfauo5k0","created":1773379734609,"text":"手动式","note":"旋钮式,拔杆式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1engnrpe80","created":1773379737567,"text":"电动式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh1en6ry3yg0","created":1773379716052,"text":"多层遮线器","note":"几组遮线板组成的遮线器,同一方向多对遮线板工作时同步活动.\n<医学影像设备学 P15>"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1en8kl5ko0","created":1773379719960,"text":"圆形照射野遮线器"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh1em403l0g0","created":1773379631650,"text":"滤线器","note":"有效消除散射线,其主要组件是滤线栅","layout_right_offset":{"x":-3.3333333791388213,"y":0},"color":"#ffffff"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1fjax0b340","created":1773382232718,"text":"固定式滤线器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fjee8muo0","created":1773382240290,"text":"活动式滤线器","note":"曝光前开始运动,曝光结束后停止,运动方向与排列方向垂直\n既能滤除散射线又不易形成铅条阴影.\n由:滤线栅,驱动机构,暗盒托盘和框架组成."},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1flb9njls0","created":1773382390211,"text":"电机式","note":"一般是凸轮电机式"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1flekz25k0","created":1773382397426,"text":"减幅振动式","note":"滤线栅由数片支撑弹簧为悬浮状态"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fm36x0qg0","created":1773382450996,"text":"储能--释放式","note":"\"弓弩\""},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fmn1zm1s0","created":1773382494233,"text":"滤线栅","note":"滤线栅(滤线栅板,滤线板)\n切割效应:滤线栅条对原发X射线的吸收作用,产生原因(滤线栅返放,横向倾斜,偏离栅焦距,焦片距超出允许范围)","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1gawfbjkg0","created":1773384395370,"text":"聚焦栅","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1fmrz3st40","created":1773382504943,"text":"结构","note":"外观为厚4~8mm的平板,内部由极薄的铅条和(纸条/木条/铝条)交替向焦排列,上下再用薄铝板封装."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1gikeo8eo0","created":1773384996123,"text":"会聚线","note":"滤线栅中心两侧的铅条向中心倾斜一定的角度,将所有铅条平面沿倾斜方向延长会聚为一条线."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1ginbgklk0","created":1773385002459,"text":"滤线栅的焦点(F)","note":"滤线栅平面中心垂直线与会聚线的相交点."},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fmul51o00","created":1773382510629,"text":"焦距(F0)","note":"(实际焦点)焦点到滤线栅中心的距离.\n80cm 90cm 100cm 120cm 150cm"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fmwzurts0","created":1773382515872,"text":"栅比(R)","note":"铅条高度与相邻铅条间隙之比.R=H/A.\n栅比越大,滤除作用越好,但对原发射线的吸收吸收量也增加.\n一般摄影--5~8(5:1~8:1)\n高千伏摄影10~12(10:1~12:1)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fn2uq4go0","created":1773382528623,"text":"栅密度(N)","note":"单位范围(cm)内所含的铅条数目.N=1/B,B--相邻铅条之间的距离.\n活动滤线栅: 20~30 L/cm\n固定滤线栅: 40 L/cm\n"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh1gb365deo0","created":1773384410053,"text":"平行栅","note":"又名线形栅,铅条纵轴排列且相互平行"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1gb4x07z40","created":1773384413854,"text":"交叉栅","note":"由两个栅焦距相等的平行栅交叉而成"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh1fwx9otfc0","created":1773383300108,"text":"注意事项","note":"滤线栅置于人体与片盒之间,聚焦面朝向X线入射方向\nX线焦点置于滤线栅的会聚线上,X线中心线可沿铅条方向倾斜,但不要垂直铅条方向倾斜.\n根据滤线栅焦距确定焦片距,其改变要小于焦距的25%\n应用活动滤线栅时,滤线栅运动时间需长于曝光时间的1/5.\n滤线栅摄影时适当增加曝光条件."},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z1mc4q5c0","created":1773335709264,"text":"固定器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z1s3chr40","created":1773335721793,"text":"压迫器"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0z1u8lqx40","created":1773335726465,"text":"高压注射器"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgxc77ct9r40","created":1772966581440,"text":"分支主题","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}